title: 820-3362-A no boot no green light
message:
Hi, got an 820-3362-A with no signs of life and no green light. No visible corrosion, wont do anything on SMC bypass. Nothing is getting hot. 

PPBUS_G3H: 12.55v

PP3V42_G3H: 3.4v

PP5V_S5: 5v

PP5V_S4: 0v

PP3V3_S5: 3.3v

PP3V3_S4: 0v

title: 820-3362-A no boot no green light
message: Do you get 3V3_SUS pressing power button?

title: 820-3362-A no boot no green light
message:
Sorry, i thought since PP3V3_S4 was 0v 3V3_SUS had to be also 0v

PP3V3_SUS is 3.3v

title: 820-3362-A no boot no green light
message: It was a bad trace around U7000. Thanks a lot.
